data.description: Presenting the Exquisite 9000 Clear Stream Lane Residence in Upper Marlboro, Maryland  Discover luxury and comfort in this impeccable townhouse nestled within the sought-after Smith Home Farm community. This home offers a spacious sanctuary with 3 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, and a versatile basement flex room.  The primary bedroom is a true retreat, featuring an expansive layout and a spa-like en-suite bathroom with a freestanding tub and separate shower.  Parking is effortless with your own 1-car garage, and the deck is ideal for outdoor living and dining. The kitchen boasts sleek stainless steel appliances and elegant wood floors.  Majestic glass rock fireplaces add warmth and sophistication to the living areas, perfect for cozy moments.  Smith Home Farm offers suburban tranquility with easy access to urban amenities. Don't miss this opportunity—schedule your viewing today and experience luxurious living in Upper Marlboro, Maryland. ***Buyer responsible for ordering  and purchasing for the HOA Resale Package****
